## Statistiques et Vues Dérivées

### Statistiques par Agent

```sql
SELECT 
  a.uid,
  a.nom,
  a.prenom,
  COUNT(t.uid) as total_transactions,
  SUM(t.montant) as montant_total,
  SUM(t.commission) as commission_totale
FROM agents a
LEFT JOIN transactions t ON a.uid = t.agent_uid
WHERE a.deleted_at IS NULL
GROUP BY a.uid;
```

### Solde Actuel par Agent

```sql
SELECT 
  a.uid,
  a.nom,
  a.prenom,
  s.espece,
  s.tmoney,
  s.flooz,
  (s.tmoney + s.flooz) as virtuel_total,
  (s.espece + s.tmoney + s.flooz) as solde_total
FROM agents a
JOIN soldes s ON a.uid = s.agent_uid
WHERE a.deleted_at IS NULL
  AND s.uid = (
    SELECT uid FROM soldes 
    WHERE agent_uid = a.uid 
    ORDER BY date DESC 
    LIMIT 1
  );
```

### Transactions par Opérateur (30 derniers jours)

```sql
SELECT 
  operateur,
  COUNT(*) as nombre_transactions,
  SUM(montant) as montant_total,
  AVG(montant) as montant_moyen,
  SUM(commission) as commission_totale
FROM transactions
WHERE date >= datetime('now', '-30 days')
  AND statut = 'validé'
GROUP BY operateur;
```

